text: Carolyn Trono (born 1 January 1961) is a Canadian rowing coxswain. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Vancouver Category:Coxswains (rowing)
